    "position": 4,
    "paragraph_or_text_span": "February 01, 2011 Full Guideline: Diagnosis and Treatment of Hyperprolactinemia: An Endocrine Society Clinical Practice Guideline JCEM February 2011 Shlomo Melmed, Felipe F. Casanueva, Andrew R. Hoffman, David L. Kleinberg, Victor M. Montori, Janet A. Schlechte, John A. H. Wass Co-Sponsoring Organizations: The European Society of Endocrinology and The Pituitary Society",
    "normalized_span_fingerprint": "26c3d9986a789bd1894acb428482de8cfc34b9f30810bb7032dd9e65a20e301c"
  },
  {
    "source_id": "endocrine-society-hyperprolactinemia-2011",
    "resolved_url": "https://www.endocrine.org/clinical-practice-guidelines/hyperprolactinemia",
    "anchor": null,
    "heading_path": [
      "Diagnosis and Treatment of Hyperprolactinemia",
      "Objective:"
    ],
    "dom_section_identifier": "endocrine-society-hyperprolactinemia-2011-section-0006",
    "position": 5,
    "paragraph_or_text_span": "The aim was to formulate practice guidelines for the diagnosis and treatment of hyperprolactinemia.",
    "normalized_span_fingerprint": "93043523b9d41f292bb69f742f44aeb6fae4932b993d88fa764833286186c6b6"
  },
  {
    "source_id": "endocrine-society-hyperprolactinemia-2011",
    "resolved_url": "https://www.endocrine.org/clinical-practice-guidelines/hyperprolactinemia",
    "anchor": null,
    "heading_path": [
      "Diagnosis and Treatment of Hyperprolactinemia",
      "Objective:",
      "Introduction:"
    ],
    "dom_section_identifier": "endocrine-society-hyperprolactinemia-2011-section-0007",
    "position": 6,
    "paragraph_or_text_span": "Testing for hyperprolactinemia is straightforward, owing to the ease of ordering a serum prolactin measurement. Accordingly, an evidence-based, cost-effective approach to management of this relatively common endocrine disorder is required.",
    "normalized_span_fingerprint": "32148804dc0371c35406d91eb702fd07d15e2a05c9556c7e81d159710661384b"
  },
  {
    "source_id": "endocrine-society-hyperprolactinemia-2011",
    "resolved_url": "https://www.endocrine.org/clinical-practice-guidelines/hyperprolactinemia",
    "anchor": null,
    "heading_path": [
      "Diagnosis and Treatment of Hyperprolactinemia",
      "Objective:",
      "Conclusions:"
    ],
    "dom_section_identifier": "endocrine-society-hyperprolactinemia-2011-section-0008",
    "position": 7,
    "paragraph_or_text_span": "Practice guidelines are presented for diagnosis and treatment of patients with elevated prolactin levels. These include: evidence-based approaches to assessing the cause of hyperprolactinemia treating drug-induced hyperprolactinemia and managing prolactinomas in nonpregnant and pregnant subjects Indications and side effects of therapeutic agents for treating prolactinomas are also presented",
    "normalized_span_fingerprint": "9e4de2e6ed52594691300283abaddf7d5186288adc900bc49b164664cecba5b2"
  },
